Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:52.84,1080CN UP,,0,0,0,,给虫玩KSP，用KOS控制发射的时候也遇到过这种情况……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:57.86,1080CN UP,,0,0,0,,“因动压过大而解体”
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.31,0:00:01.31,1080CN,,0,0,0,,哈喽啊
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.31,0:00:01.31,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.96,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这个YouTuber叫Xavier，是个开发者，字幕翻译给虫
Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.96,1080EN,,0,0,0,,My name is Xavier and as you might know I’m a developer.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.96,0:00:09.56,1080CN,,0,0,0,,但同时还是个SpaceX的粉丝，所以我在想，猎鹰9号、重型猎鹰和龙飞船
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.96,0:00:09.56,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But I’m also a huge SpaceX fan and that got me thinking: what software and hardware
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.15,1080CN,,0,0,0,,上硬件和软件是啥样的？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.15,1080EN,,0,0,0,,powers the Falcon 9, Falcon Heavy and Dragon?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.15,0:00:17.26,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我们首先看看飞船上的软件与硬件飞行时要面临哪些问题
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.15,0:00:17.26,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Let’s first take a look at what challenges the hardware and software of a spacecraft
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.26,0:00:20.85,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我们首先看看飞船上的软件与硬件飞行时要面临哪些问题
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.26,0:00:20.85,1080EN,,0,0,0,,faces when it is being launched into space.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.94,1080CN,,0,0,0,,首先想要让东西进入地球轨道是很难的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.94,1080EN,,0,0,0,,First of all its very hard to get your craft into orbit around the earth.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.94,0:00:30.02,1080CN,,0,0,0,,火箭上震动会很剧烈，使得飞船本身
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.94,0:00:30.02,1080EN,,0,0,0,,A launch on top of a rocket causes a lot of vibrations and that means that the craft itself
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.02,0:00:33.91,1080CN,,0,0,0,,和上面的电子设备要能经受得住
Dialogue: 2,0:00:30.02,0:00:33.91,1080EN,,0,0,0,,and the electronics have to be able to withstand that.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.91,0:00:38.18,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而当你进了太空以后，难题就更多了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:33.91,0:00:38.18,1080EN,,0,0,0,,And once you get in orbit, you are welcomed by even more challenges.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.18,0:00:42.86,1080CN,,0,0,0,,太阳直射时龙飞船要忍受阳面的热量
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.18,0:00:42.86,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Dragon for instance has to be able to cope with intense heat when it’s facing the sun
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.86,0:00:47.07,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而到了地球背面则要忍受低温
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.86,0:00:47.07,1080EN,,0,0,0,,but also intense cold when sunlight is blocked by earth.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.07,0:00:53.42,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这个温度变化在-150摄氏度到120摄氏度
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.07,0:00:53.42,1080EN,,0,0,0,,These temperatures range from -150°C all the way up to 120°C
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.42,0:00:57.00,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而对于电子设备，最大的问题来自于辐射
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.42,0:00:57.00,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But the biggest problem for the electronics is radiation.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.00,0:01:02.57,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这种辐射来自于太阳、地球磁场，甚至来自外太阳系的粒子与射线
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.00,0:01:02.57,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This radiation comes from high-energy particles that are ejected by our sun, particles trapped
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.57,0:01:09.09,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这种辐射来自于太阳、地球磁场、甚至来自外太阳系的粒子与射线
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.57,0:01:09.09,1080EN,,0,0,0,,in Earth’s magnetic field and even cosmic rays or particles from outside our solar system.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.09,0:01:13.51,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这些粒子会对飞船上的电子系统产生严重影响
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.09,0:01:13.51,1080EN,,0,0,0,,These particles can have pretty severe effects on the systems inside a spacecraft.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.51,0:01:17.67,1080CN,,0,0,0,,其中最大的问题是比特反转
Dialogue: 2,0:01:13.51,0:01:17.67,1080EN,,0,0,0,,One of the biggest problems is whats called a bit flip.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.67,0:01:23.63,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这发生在高能粒子击中飞船的内存或者处理器时
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.67,0:01:23.63,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This occurs when a high energy particle hits the memory or the processor of the spacecraft.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.63,0:01:30.22,1080CN,,0,0,0,,击中内存，可能把0打成1了，最终让一块内存崩溃
Dialogue: 2,0:01:23.63,0:01:30.22,1080EN,,0,0,0,,If it hits the memory it can cause a 0 to become a 1, essentially corrupting a part of the memory.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.36,1080CN,,0,0,0,,幸好SpaceX飞船上的软件能够检测到这种比特反转
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.36,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Luckily though the software onboard SpaceX vehicles can detect these bit flips and fix
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.52,1080CN,,0,0,0,,并通过奇偶校验修正之
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.52,1080EN,,0,0,0,,the corrupted memory by using parity bits.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.11,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这点问题不大
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.11,1080EN,,0,0,0,,No big deal.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.11,0:01:46.72,1080CN,,0,0,0,,然而当处理器被击中，则会导致计算结果完全错误
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.11,0:01:46.72,1080EN,,0,0,0,,However when the processor is hit with radiation it can cause the result of a calculation to be completely incorrect.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.06,0:01:51.81,1080CN,,0,0,0,,举个简单的例子，我们让处理器计算10+10
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.06,0:01:51.81,1080EN,,0,0,0,,To demonstrate this, let’s ask a processor to calculate 10+10.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.81,0:01:55.78,1080CN,,0,0,0,,二进制是这样的，结果是20(二进制的10100)
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.81,0:01:55.78,1080EN,,0,0,0,,In binary that would look like this and the result is obviously 20.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.56,1080CN,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.56,1080EN,,0,0,0,,No surprises there!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.56,0:02:02.92,1080CN,,0,0,0,,但如果计算这个式子时发生了比特反转，我们看看结果会如何
Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.56,0:02:02.92,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But let’s now take a look at what happens when a bit flip occurs while performing this calculation.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.17,0:02:08.87,1080CN,,0,0,0,,还是让处理器计算10+10，但由于处理器内发生了比特反转
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.17,0:02:08.87,1080EN,,0,0,0,,We still ask the processor to calculate 10 + 10 but because of the bit flip the processor
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.87,0:02:12.43,1080CN,,0,0,0,,计算的内容就完全不是那回事了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.87,0:02:12.43,1080EN,,0,0,0,,is actually calculating something completely different.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.43,0:02:19.07,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而最终结果就是10+10=24
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.43,0:02:19.07,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Right now it will say that 10 + 10 equals 24 because one of the bits flipped while running the calculations…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.78,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这种计算错误会对飞船造成极其严重的后果
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.78,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Wrong calculations can have very severe effects on a spacecraft.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.78,0:02:29.37,1080CN,,0,0,0,,1996年阿里安5火箭首飞
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.78,0:02:29.37,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This was demonstrated by the maiden flight of the Ariane 5 rocket in 1996.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.37,0:02:34.62,1080CN,,0,0,0,,它虽然没有遇到比特反转，但在飞行40秒时，火箭上的软件
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.37,0:02:34.62,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It didn’t suffer from a bit flip, but 40 seconds into the flight, the rocket’s software
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.62,0:02:41.03,1080CN,,0,0,0,,想把一个64位的数字存进16位的地址中，导致数字被截断
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.62,0:02:41.03,1080EN,,0,0,0,,tried to put a 64 bit number into a 16 bit address causing the number to be truncated
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.95,1080CN,,0,0,0,,从而得到一个完全不同的结果
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.95,1080EN,,0,0,0,,and be completely different.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.95,0:02:47.20,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而火箭航电设备依然按照这个错误结果继续运算
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.95,0:02:47.20,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The rocket’s avionics then continued to perform their calculations with this wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.20,0:02:52.84,1080CN,,0,0,0,,然后飞着飞着突然改变航向，因为火箭以为自己飞错方向了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.20,0:02:52.84,1080EN,,0,0,0,,number and performed an abrupt course correction because it thought it was going to wrong way.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.84,0:02:57.86,1080CN,,0,0,0,,火箭最终说白了就是被风吹散架了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.84,0:02:57.86,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The vehicle eventually broke up because the aerodynamic stress was simply too high.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.86,0:03:02.21,1080CN,,0,0,0,,回到SpaceX上来，他们如何处理辐射问题呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.86,0:03:02.21,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Now back to SpaceX: how do they handle the problem of radiation?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.21,0:03:06.84,1080CN,,0,0,0,,他们假设电子设备无法完全避免辐射
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.21,0:03:06.84,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Well they assume that you can’t protect electronics completely from radiation and
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.73,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这是他们系统设计的思路
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.73,1080EN,,0,0,0,,they design their systems with this in mind.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.73,0:03:15.40,1080CN,,0,0,0,,他们不选昂贵的抗辐射零件，而是现成的零件
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.73,0:03:15.40,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Instead of using expensive, radiation-hardened parts, SpaceX uses off-the-shelf components.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.69,1080CN,,0,0,0,,比如龙飞船
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.69,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Let’s look at Dragon first.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.69,0:03:23.40,1080CN,,0,0,0,,根据John Muratore，前SpaceX载具保障说，每一艘龙飞船
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.69,0:03:23.40,1080EN,,0,0,0,,According to John Muratore, previous director of SpaceX vehicle certification, each Dragon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.40,0:03:26.01,1080CN,,0,0,0,,有三台飞行计算机
Dialogue: 2,0:03:23.40,0:03:26.01,1080EN,,0,0,0,,is equipped with three flight computers.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.01,0:03:30.76,1080CN,,0,0,0,,每台飞行计算机由两个x86处理器驱动
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.01,0:03:30.76,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Each of these flight computers is powered by a dual core x86 processor.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.76,0:03:34.81,1080CN,,0,0,0,,计算机本身并不是多核运算的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.76,0:03:34.81,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The computers however don’t use the multicore capability.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.81,0:03:41.18,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而是每个计算在每个核上独立进行一次，然后对比结果
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.81,0:03:41.18,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Instead they execute each calculation on the two cores individually and compare the results.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.18,0:03:46.27,1080CN,,0,0,0,,所以三台计算机，每台两个核心，就有6个结果
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.18,0:03:46.27,1080EN,,0,0,0,,So three flight computer with each a dual core processor can be seen as 6 independent
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.27,0:03:50.17,1080CN,,0,0,0,,然后互相检查计算结果
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.27,0:03:50.17,1080EN,,0,0,0,,computers that are constantly checking each others calculations.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.17,0:03:54.89,1080CN,,0,0,0,,如果某台计算机遭到比特反转，得出了错误结果
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.17,0:03:54.89,1080EN,,0,0,0,,If one of the flight computers is hit with radiation and produces a wrong calculation,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.94,1080CN,,0,0,0,,其他的计算机就会发现
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.94,1080EN,,0,0,0,,the others will spot it.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.94,0:04:02.30,1080CN,,0,0,0,,此时，那台出错的计算机就会自动重启，防止后续错误的发生
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.94,0:04:02.30,1080EN,,0,0,0,,When that happens the malfunctioning computer will be rebooted automatically to prevent further errors.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.58,0:04:06.51,1080CN,,0,0,0,,重启后，计算机要进行一次“再同步”
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.58,0:04:06.51,1080EN,,0,0,0,,After rebooting the computer has to perform whats called a re-sync.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.51,0:04:11.09,1080CN,,0,0,0,,要让它跟上飞船当前的任务，所以直接从另外两台计算机内存里复制内容然后继续跑程序
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.51,0:04:11.09,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It has to get up to speed with what the vehicle is doing, so it copies the memory of the other
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.09,0:04:14.06,1080CN,,0,0,0,,要让它跟上飞船当前的任务，所以直接从另外两台计算机内存里复制内容然后继续跑程序
Dialogue: 2,0:04:11.09,0:04:14.06,1080EN,,0,0,0,,two computers and runs the same programs.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.06,0:04:19.37,1080CN,,0,0,0,,有点像电脑上“重启后恢复所有窗口”那个选项
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.06,0:04:19.37,1080EN,,0,0,0,,A bit like rebooting your computer with the option to restore all your windows when you log back in.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.89,0:04:24.88,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而龙飞船还能应付这三台计算机同时全部被辐射击中的情况
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.89,0:04:24.88,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Dragon can even handle a situation where all three of its computers are hit by radiation
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.22,1080CN,,0,0,0,,虽然这种情况发生概率极低
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.22,1080EN,,0,0,0,,at the same time although thats very unlikely to happen.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.22,0:04:35.32,1080CN,,0,0,0,,除了这三台飞行计算机，龙飞船还有另外18套系统，也都是三冗余设计
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.22,0:04:35.32,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Besides 3 flight computers, Dragon has 18 other systems onboard that also use triple redundancy computers.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.34,1080CN,,0,0,0,,总共处理器数量就达到了54！
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.34,1080EN,,0,0,0,,That brings the total amount of processors up to 54!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.83,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这还只是龙飞船上的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.83,1080EN,,0,0,0,,And that’s just for a single Dragon capsule.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.83,0:04:46.80,1080CN,,0,0,0,,除了龙飞船，猎鹰9号火箭也有冗余系统
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.83,0:04:46.80,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But Dragon isn’t alone, also the Falcon 9 has redundant systems.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.80,0:04:51.53,1080CN,,0,0,0,,九台发动机，每台三部计算机，每部计算机三冗余
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.80,0:04:51.53,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It has 3 computers for each engine (9 x 3) and triple-redundancy flight computer which
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.53,0:04:54.88,1080CN,,0,0,0,,加上主控计算机，就是三十个处理器
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.53,0:04:54.88,1080EN,,0,0,0,,means that it carries 30 processors.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.72,1080CN,,0,0,0,,至少2012年是这样的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.72,1080EN,,0,0,0,,At least that was the situation in 2012.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.72,0:05:03.56,1080CN,,0,0,0,,目前来看，猎鹰9为了着陆可能还要装更多的处理器
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.72,0:05:03.56,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Right now it’s possible that Falcon 9 has even more processors to handle the landing.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.12,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这时候你可能会问……
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.12,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Now at this point you might be thinking: hang on…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.12,0:05:10.80,1080CN,,0,0,0,,NASA真的允许SpaceX用普通民用的硬件设备吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.12,0:05:10.80,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Does NASA really allow SpaceX to use regular hardware components?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.38,1080CN,,0,0,0,,就是那种你我在淘宝都能买到的？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.38,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The ones you and I can buy on Amazon?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.81,1080CN,,0,0,0,,呃……还真就是！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.81,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Well actually yes!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.81,0:05:19.03,1080CN,,0,0,0,,NASA并不强求使用抗辐射设备
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.81,0:05:19.03,1080EN,,0,0,0,,NASA doesn’t require the use of radiation-hardened components.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.03,0:05:25.22,1080CN,,0,0,0,,但他们会要求SpaceX广泛调查辐射对飞船的影响
Dialogue: 2,0:05:19.03,0:05:25.22,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Instead they require SpaceX to do extensive research into what effects the radiation can have on their spacecrafts.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.78,0:05:29.44,1080CN,,0,0,0,,如果知道了影响是怎样的，那就有解决办法了
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.78,0:05:29.44,1080EN,,0,0,0,,If they know how they’ll be affected, they can compensate for it.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.44,0:05:35.82,1080CN,,0,0,0,,实际上这叫“耐辐射”设计，和“抗辐射”设计是不同的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.44,0:05:35.82,1080EN,,0,0,0,,In fact this is called a radiation-tolerant design and is different from a radiation-hardened design.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.22,0:05:40.35,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而且实际上NASA自己都不会在所有地方使用抗辐射的设备
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.22,0:05:40.35,1080EN,,0,0,0,,In fact NASA itself doesn’t use radiation-hardened parts everywhere.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.35,0:05:45.03,1080CN,,0,0,0,,国际空间站上目前就是各种混合设备
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.35,0:05:45.03,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The International Space Station for instance uses a mix of radiation-hardened parts but
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.03,0:05:49.02,1080CN,,0,0,0,,一些控制甚至用的是普通的笔记本电脑
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.03,0:05:49.02,1080EN,,0,0,0,,they also use regular laptops for some controls.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.02,0:05:55.05,1080CN,,0,0,0,,航天飞机上的一些设备也是耐辐射而不是抗辐射的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.02,0:05:55.05,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Even some parts on the Space Shuttle were radiation-tolerant instead of radiation-hardened.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.05,0:05:58.21,1080CN,,0,0,0,,回到SpaceX，他们怎么选零件呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.05,0:05:58.21,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But back to SpaceX: how do they select their parts?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.21,0:06:02.74,1080CN,,0,0,0,,两个条件，第一是要满足火箭、飞船的需求
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.21,0:06:02.74,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Well they have two conditions: first of all the parts have to be capable enough to handle
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.74,0:06:09.72,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这点不必多言；第二是要有合适的Tooling
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.74,0:06:09.72,1080EN,,0,0,0,,their tasks - pretty obvious - and secondly, they take into account what tooling is available for that particular part.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.81,1080CN,,0,0,0,,Tooling指的是SpaceX能雇佣哪些人
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.81,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Tooling determines what kind of people SpaceX can hire.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.81,0:06:20.15,1080CN,,0,0,0,,现成的硬件，通用性强，对应的软件与开发工具也有很多开发者在用
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.81,0:06:20.15,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Off-the-shelf hardware is pretty generic and uses software and tooling that a lot of developers already know.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.65,0:06:24.26,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这让SpaceX不用费太大劲去找优秀的工程师
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.65,0:06:24.26,1080EN,,0,0,0,,And that means that SpaceX has less trouble finding great engineers.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.26,0:06:29.75,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而抗辐射设备，本身用的就少，上面的编程语言和开发工具也鲜有人知
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.26,0:06:29.75,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Radiation hardened parts however only work with special programming languages that few
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.75,0:06:34.57,1080CN,,0,0,0,,使得SpaceX就很难招揽人才
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.75,0:06:34.57,1080EN,,0,0,0,,people know, thus limiting the ability to hire new people.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.57,0:06:39.28,1080CN,,0,0,0,,同时现成的硬件还很便宜，SpaceX可以更广泛的进行测试
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.57,0:06:39.28,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Off-the-shelf hardware is also cheaper and that allows SpaceX to extensively test these systems.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.28,0:06:45.40,1080CN,,0,0,0,,John Muratore说一个人办公桌上放过40片飞行计算机芯片用于测试
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.28,0:06:45.40,1080EN,,0,0,0,,John Muratore said that at one point over 40 flight computers were sitting on people’s
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.75,1080CN,,0,0,0,,John Muratore说一个人办公桌上放过40片飞行计算机芯片用于测试
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.75,1080EN,,0,0,0,,desks for testing and development.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.78,1080CN,,0,0,0,,换又贵又少的芯片就没法这么做
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.78,1080EN,,0,0,0,,You simply cannot do that with expensive and hard to come by hardware.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.78,0:06:55.68,1080CN,,0,0,0,,硬件说得差不多，那控制各种东西的软件又如何呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.78,0:06:55.68,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But enough about all this hardware, what about the software that controls everything?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.68,0:06:59.21,1080CN,,0,0,0,,呃SpaceX选择的操作系统是Linux
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.68,0:06:59.21,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Well the operating system of choice at SpaceX is Linux.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.21,0:07:03.69,1080CN,,0,0,0,,工程师电脑上和火箭上都是Linux系统
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.21,0:07:03.69,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It runs on the desktops of the engineers and powers its vehicles.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.69,0:07:10.00,1080CN,,0,0,0,,它们都用Linux能简化开发流程，同时也带来了整套齐全的工具
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.69,0:07:10.00,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Using Linux everywhere allows them to streamline the development process and use the robust tools that come with it.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.53,0:07:15.94,1080CN,,0,0,0,,编程语言用的是C++，原因有二
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.53,0:07:15.94,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The programming language of choice is C++ and they use it for two main reasons.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.94,0:07:22.02,1080CN,,0,0,0,,第一，C++用的人还算多，所以SpaceX招人方便
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.94,0:07:22.02,1080EN,,0,0,0,,First it allows SpaceX to hire a lot of brilliant people because the language is still relatively popular.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.58,1080CN,,0,0,0,,第二，C++的生态很棒
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.58,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Secondly, they benefits from the large C++ ecosystem.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.58,0:07:31.06,1080CN,,0,0,0,,不用费劲自己造轮子，好多工具像gcc、gdb都是现成的
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.58,0:07:31.06,1080EN,,0,0,0,,No need to create custom software when you can just use tools that developers already
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.56,1080CN,,0,0,0,,不用费劲自己造轮子，好多工具像gcc、gdb都是现成的
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.56,1080EN,,0,0,0,,know like gcc, and gdb for instance.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.56,0:07:37.56,1080CN,,0,0,0,,但也不是只用Linux
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.56,0:07:37.56,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But Linux isn’t the only platform that is being used.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.56,0:07:42.88,1080CN,,0,0,0,,他们还用Windows平台的LabView，一个图形化编程工具
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.56,0:07:42.88,1080EN,,0,0,0,,They also use LabView a graphical programming tool that runs on Windows.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.88,0:07:48.37,1080CN,,0,0,0,,功能是在猎鹰9或者龙飞船飞行时可视化遥测数据
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.88,0:07:48.37,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It is used to visualise telemetry that they get from a Falcon 9 or Dragon during flight.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.37,0:07:52.90,1080CN,,0,0,0,,地面小组用它监督重要数据
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.37,0:07:52.90,1080EN,,0,0,0,,And ground teams use it to keep an eye on important metrics.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.90,0:07:58.15,1080CN,,0,0,0,,另外值得注意的是，SpaceX会尽量保持代码在不同载具间的通用性
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.90,0:07:58.15,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Another interesting fact is that SpaceX tries to share as much code as possible between its vehicles.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.35,0:08:05.05,1080CN,,0,0,0,,最大的好处是某种载具的bug修正后，其他载具上的代码也能被push掉
Dialogue: 2,0:07:58.35,0:08:05.05,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The biggest advantage of this is that bug fixes for one vehicle are automatically pushed to the other vehicles as well.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.34,0:08:10.94,1080CN,,0,0,0,,还有，SpaceX很欢迎游戏开发者
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.34,0:08:10.94,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Oh and another interesting fact is that game developers are usually a good fit for SpaceX
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.94,0:08:16.90,1080CN,,0,0,0,,因为他们都已习惯在存储容量、计算性能受限的环境下开发
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.94,0:08:16.90,1080EN,,0,0,0,,because they are used to writing code that runs in environments where memory and processing power are constrained.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.47,0:08:23.18,1080CN,,0,0,0,,最后说说SpaceX如何监测他们的软件和载具
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.47,0:08:23.18,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The last thing we’ll take a look at is how SpaceX monitors their software and vehicles.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.18,0:08:27.29,1080CN,,0,0,0,,工程师会在所有能想到的地方加系统指标
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.18,0:08:27.29,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Engineers are encouraged to add Metrics to everything they can think about.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.29,0:08:32.29,1080CN,,0,0,0,,当载具运行时，会收集所有log，然后会有程序分析这些log
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.29,0:08:32.29,1080EN,,0,0,0,,When a vehicle is being used, all these logs are collected and analysed by programs who
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.29,0:08:36.02,1080CN,,0,0,0,,一旦哪项超过安全阈值就会报警
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.29,0:08:36.02,1080EN,,0,0,0,,raise an alarm if something is not within the safety margins.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.03,0:08:41.40,1080CN,,0,0,0,,所有系统指标都和运行时的源代码保存在一起
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.03,0:08:41.40,1080EN,,0,0,0,,All these metrics are stored together with the source code that was running at that time.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.40,0:08:46.05,1080CN,,0,0,0,,一旦出现问题，SpaceX就能重现适当的情况
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.40,0:08:46.05,1080EN,,0,0,0,,If something goes wrong with the vehicle, SpaceX can recreate the exact environment
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.05,0:08:49.25,1080CN,,0,0,0,,再现问题并解决
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.05,0:08:49.25,1080EN,,0,0,0,,to reproduce the problem and fix it.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.25,0:08:54.05,1080CN,,0,0,0,,最后，他们还用持续集成的方法，自动测试所有工程师提交的代码
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.25,0:08:54.05,1080EN,,0,0,0,,And finally they are using continuous integration to automatically test all the code that is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.00,1080CN,,0,0,0,,最后，他们还用持续集成的方法，自动测试所有工程师提交的代码
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.00,1080EN,,0,0,0,,being written by the engineers.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.00,0:09:01.93,1080CN,,0,0,0,,他们还会把猎鹰9用的所有零件都连上，从而模拟
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.00,0:09:01.93,1080EN,,0,0,0,,They even have test stands with all the components of a Falcon 9 bolted on so they can simulate
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.93,0:09:06.27,1080CN,,0,0,0,,一次完整的飞行过程，发现潜在问题
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.93,0:09:06.27,1080EN,,0,0,0,,a complete flight to discover potential problems.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.27,0:09:10.99,1080CN,,0,0,0,,关于软硬件的更多细节也没了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.27,0:09:10.99,1080EN,,0,0,0,,More details about the used hardware and software aren’t really available and that’s because
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.99,0:09:14.39,1080CN,,0,0,0,,因为美国政府认为这些是机密
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.99,0:09:14.39,1080EN,,0,0,0,,the United States government considers it classified.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.39,0:09:19.07,1080CN,,0,0,0,,猎鹰9这种火箭其实就是能上太空的导弹
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.39,0:09:19.07,1080EN,,0,0,0,,A rocket like the Falcon 9 is basically a missile that goes to space.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.07,0:09:23.81,1080CN,,0,0,0,,落入坏蛋手中不一定闹出什么幺蛾子
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.07,0:09:23.81,1080EN,,0,0,0,,So in the wrong hands, the technology could be misused and cause harm.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.81,0:09:28.37,1080CN,,0,0,0,,但即使这样我们也能大致很好的了解SpaceX使用的软硬件设备
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.81,0:09:28.37,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But even with limited information we got a pretty good view at what software and hardware
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.37,0:09:32.20,1080CN,,0,0,0,,与这些设备在恶劣太空环境中要面对的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.37,0:09:32.20,1080EN,,0,0,0,,is being used at SpaceX and what challenges the teams face, considering the harsh environment in space.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.32,1080CN,,0,0,0,,就酱啦
Dialogue: 2,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.32,1080EN,,0,0,0,,That was it for this video!
